overview: Are you ready? Then give me a "hell yeah!" Relive one of the greatest periods in sports-entertainment history with WWE Attitude Era Unreleased Volume 3. This release contains even more attitude and features over 7 hours of exclusive never- before-seen matches and moments featuring: Stone Cold Steve Austin, The Rock, Undertaker, Triple H, Shawn Michaels, Bret "Hit Man" Hart, Mick Foley, and all your favorite Attitude Era Superstars!
title: WWE: Attitude Era: Vol. 3 Unreleased
